I believe I kind of overlooked at this, I remember we discussed with @parlt91 but then we never got back on this. Probably in this case it will be a bit of overengineering work to use the existing component, but we really should. User will never need to use Table.js component feature (ordering by column, comparing values, etc) but it is important to keep every table look&feel fetching structure from the same piece of code.
@parlt91 if you need any help to adapt and make use of the existing table component, just ping me. I think we really should do this now that we have "a bit of time" 😉
